<p class="title">Use Case Admin</p>
<br>
<p>A complaint has been logged in the messaging system about an inappropriate listing of an item.  James Dean looks at his email and sees that the user who posted has refused to unlist the item.</p>
<p>He logs into the site and goes into the admin area and pulls up the users account and info.  As per the site use agreement, admin have the right to remove users if they refuse to unlist inappropriate items.  He sets the user profile in the database so that they can no longer buy or sell on the site.</p>